_sText:
Just a small map for warm up.

Materials, Sounds and Models used: CSS/HL2
Construction time: app. 6 hours

Gameplay: Both teams spawn with their regular guns (glock, usp) and can either stay in their base, trying to get ahold of an AWP lying there, or rush forward and try to pick up their own teams respective weapons (Galil/FAMAS, Uzi/TMP, AK/M4). There are no buyzones.
